Installation Instructions
-------------------------

* Unpack the spiff archive.

* Copy spiff to your webserver.

* Grant all permissions on libs/smarty/templates_c to the webserver.
  This is done by either using your FTP client (refer to the documentation
  of the client in that case), or with shell access by issuing the following
  command:

  chmod 777 spiff/libs/smarty/templates_c/
  
* Copy spiff/admin/config.inc.php.tmpl to spiff/admin/config.inc.php.

* Edit spiff/admin/config.inc.php according to your webserver configuration.
  The file should be self explaining.

* Open spiff/libs/phpgacl-vx.x.x/setup.php in your web browser and follow
  the instructions (if any).

* Open spiff/libs/phpgacl-vx.x.x/admin/acl_admin in your web browser and
  make sure that no error message appears.

* Open spiff/admin/setup.php in your web browser and make sure that no
  error message appears.
  !!! WARNING: This step will erase the content of the database that
      was configured in spiff/admin/config.inc.php !!!

* Done. You should now be able to open spiff/index.php in your web browser.
